BFN 

  [Text] A responsible Palestinian source within Fatah has 
told AL-WATAN AL-'ARABI that he doubts that all of the 
resistance operations that have been carried out against the 
Israelis in the occupied territories are the making of Hamas, as 
Israel declares. 
  The source said Fatah fighters are still practicing 
resistance to pressure the Israelis and are carrying out 
military operations. The source said that the person who carried 
out the 'Afula operation was from Fatah [see 13 April Terrorism 
Report]. 
  Last week, the chief of the Israeli police said that the 
Palestinian youth who carried out an operation in Jerusalem was 
a Hamas member, but it turned out later that he was a Fatah 
supporter who wanted to avenge the death of a friend killed by 
the Israelis a few days before near Jerusalem. 

