<H3> <TI>   New Federal Public Prosecutor on RAF, Luebeck Synagogue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Federal Public Prosecutor on RAF, Luebeck Synagogue </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0205172494 Hamburg BILD AM SONNTAG in German 1 May 94 p 4 </F>
