<H3> <TI>   Kidnapped Sudanese Envoy to Somalia Released </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kidnapped Sudanese Envoy to Somalia Released </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA2704120094 Khartoum SUNA in English 1004 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> EA2704120094 </F>
<F P=104>  Khartoum SUNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Addis Ababa, 27 Apr (SUNA) -- 'Abd-al-Baqi Muhammad 
Hasan, Sudan's ambassador to Mogadishu town [was] released 
today. Hasan was abducted recently by three Somali gunmen from 
[the] Hawadle clan. 
  [Paris AFP in English at 1115 GMT on 27 April, in a 
Nairobi-datelined item, adds: "Somali gunmen released unharmed 
and without conditions Sudan's ambassador to Mogadishu following 
intervention by Somali faction leaders, diplomats said Tuesday. 
Hasan was freed after Sudanese officials who went to Mogadishu 
last week requested some undisclosed Somali politicians to help 
secure his release, said a diplomat who asked not to be named. 
The ambassador was `in good condition' and joked about having 
gained weight during his eight days in captivity."] 

</TEXT>

