<H3> <TI>   Former PKK Official Attacked in Germany </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Former PKK Official Attacked in Germany </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0405112394 Hamburg DPA in German 1039 GMT 4 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0405112394 </F>
<F P=104>  Hamburg DPA </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


